{"tid":1721340,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發：人權法案即將通過！已正式開始通過「Senate Hotline」程序！距離通過又近了一步！","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T16:45:23.000Z","uid":293289,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"8ecb70aa343024c4a6fc1e3ba569d1d4b148ff87","tid":1721340,"uid":293289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:35:46.000Z","msg":"🇺🇸法案最新消息！！美國參議員Josh Hawley：￼人權法案即將通過！正式開始通過「Senate Hotline」程序！距離通過又近了一步！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t2525Gq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft2525Gq.png&h=149add89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n#StandWithHongKong<br />\n<br />\n入去推&amp;RT: <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1194998439723065345?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345%3Fs%3D21&d=zfTWtzkQ24d%2FEmJzkWMc6zH2jDdsOF1PL3r%2FkI4IfR4%3D&h=1d765f7d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhawleymo%2Fstatus%2F1194998439723065345%3Fs%3D21&h=a2109858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/hawleymo/status/1194998439723065345?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n（狠人繼續呼籲：大家唔好鬆懈￼，繼續堅守崗位做國際文宣！！！）￼<br />\n<br />\nPS：「Senate Hotline（熱線）」表決方式毋須佔用大會討論時間，是參議院常見取得議員「一致同意」的非正式方式，令法案最快可在下周內通過。「熱線」方式需要審議相關法案的委員會主席一同提出，而有關方式意指多數黨及少數黨領袖在參議院「衣帽間」放出有關擬議法案的通知，透過電郵或電話通知各議員，徵詢意向，反對者需在一定時限內提出異議，若無人反對，最快可在感恩節假期前的大會會期（22日）內宣佈通過。據知，若以「熱線」方式進行，則法案內容不會作出改動。"},{"pid":"5e430262ffcc5f4196565ec9f5c706095917bdeb","tid":1721340,"uid":190793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:37:07.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4ddacb345566d78aa99026c9f80bfcb5ce1ce82e","tid":1721340,"uid":3553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:38:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/no